eive hints to complete the game.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/b6be5985570236974ef697d065a27346.poster.avif?t=1732729791\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/b6be5985570236974ef697d065a27346.webm?t=1732729791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/b6be5985570236974ef697d065a27346.mp4?t=1732729791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape from the monster in the circle of the holy altar. Find matches by exploring the village and light the candles on the altar to activate the protection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/7bf9fa20e56f8491fa0c3f559c340773.poster.avif?t=1732729791\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/7bf9fa20e56f8491fa0c3f559c340773.webm?t=1732729791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/7bf9fa20e56f8491fa0c3f559c340773.mp4?t=1732729791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/d90f440fe29e8cedb47887c4f222a55e.avif?t=1732729791\" width=620 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. The game has autosave.</p><p class=\"bb